\f1\fs28 P!NG User Manual\f0\fs22\par
\par

\f1\fs24 1. Overview\f0\fs22\par
\par
P!NG is an impulse response (IR) reverb plugin for macOS. It convolves your audio with IR files to add reverb, and includes a built-in IR synthesiser to generate new IRs from room geometry, materials, and speaker/mic placement.\par
\par
\line \par

